**Note:** Before applying this configuration, you must:
1. Replace the placeholder subnet IDs (`subnet-12345678`, etc.) with your actual VPC subnet IDs
2. Replace the placeholder security group ID (`sg-1234567890abcdef0`) with your actual security group ID
3. Ensure the subnets are in at least 2 different AZs for MSK high availability
4. The security group must allow inbound traffic on Kafka ports (9092, 9094, etc.)

